COPS in Cape Town arrested an unknown man driving at speeds
of more than 250 km/h in his Lamborghini Gallardo on the N1 between Sable Road and
Plattekloof.According to the City of Cape Town, the driver was taken
into custody on Monday morning.The driver has been charged with reckless and negligent
